題係如果港航d人買左保險，點出到市區...<br />\n個陣旅遊巴全個擋風玻璃都白色係哂雪，搭的士會唔會更危險（30分鐘車程有d玩命feel咁）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買左保險既正確處理方法應該係出去住酒店claim錢定留機場訓claim食飯錢<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448d160ffb52a59f54920ee953ba8c895cdbb55a","tid":52005,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:41:09.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5dff831b6d09d55390b32a62637c52b823cfa74","tid":52005,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:00:14.000Z","msg":"冬天去 預咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1395aa4063e2bdcfa15a7f818746fa33b3c944dd","tid":52005,"uid":17324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:06:06.000Z","msg":"隔離Post 個巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20897627c4fc9bcc90198f9c199a14b9e5e19d0f","tid":52005,"uid":47027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:15:21.000Z","msg":"港航做特價去北海道連稅三千八仲包行李，平過廉航，用下腦都知有保障喇。有買旅行保咪冇事囉。"},{"pid":"06007ebaa5e6f0e716901f4675e33c6e94525c74","tid":52005,"uid":47027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港航做特價去北海道連稅三千八仲包行李，平過廉航，用下腦都知冇保障喇。有買旅行保咪冇事囉。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4c45d83a04e077fe0e5b41f31844a8d59fa02b63","tid":52005,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:15:06.000Z","msg":"架佬d機場管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbda9795f53797fb3e9f7a53e7accc305c3a1db","tid":52005,"uid":9410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:17:21.000Z","msg":"冬天去落雪地方一定要買旅保啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩事都包飛包食住"}]}